<heading id="3E1D4846FFE7FFD8FF71FF44FD9CFF1E" bold="true" box="[151,609,150,177]" fontSize="11" level="2" pageId="15" pageNumber="16" reason="4">
<taxonomicName id="A2EA84A9FFE7FFD8FF71FF44FD9CFF1E" authority="(Yoshimoto, 1999)" baseAuthorityName="Yoshimoto" baseAuthorityYear="1999" box="[151,609,150,177]" class="Insecta" family="Noctuidae" genus="Eudocima" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="15" pageNumber="16" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="splendida">
<emphasis id="579E2338FFE7FFD8FF71FF44FD9CFF1E" bold="true" box="[151,609,150,177]" pageId="15" pageNumber="16">
<emphasis id="579E2338FFE7FFD8FF71FF44FE7FFF1F" bold="true" box="[151,386,150,177]" italics="true" pageId="15" pageNumber="16">Eudocima splendida</emphasis>
(
<bibRefCitation id="017B82DBFFE7FFD8FE77FF44FDA5FF1E" author="Yoshimoto, H." box="[401,600,150,176]" pageId="15" pageNumber="16" pagination="60 - 62" refId="ref41277" refString="Yoshimoto, H. (1999) A new species of the genus Othreis Hubner (Noctuidae, Ophiderinae) from Myanmar. Transactions of the Lepidopterological Society of Japan, 50 (1), 60 - 62." type="journal article" year="1999">Yoshimoto, 1999</bibRefCitation>
)
</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
</heading>
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="2DF0ACA1FFE7FFD8FF71FF68FED0FECA" pageId="15" pageNumber="16" type="description">
<paragraph id="6555FF2AFFE7FFD8FF71FF68FE4BFF7B" blockId="15.[151,1437,150,357]" box="[151,438,186,213]" pageId="15" pageNumber="16">
(
<figureCitation id="FDD1E3AFFFE7FFD8FF79FF68FF14FF7A" box="[159,233,186,212]" captionStart="FIGURE 8" captionStartId="61.[151,250,1953,1977]" captionTargetBox="[256,1329,189,1922]" captionTargetId="figure-19@61.[247,1340,181,1929]" captionTargetPageId="61" captionText="FIGURE 8. Eudocima kinabaluenis and Eudocima homaena group adults (dorsal aspect)." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6605514" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6605514/files/figure.png" pageId="15" pageNumber="16">Figs 8</figureCitation>
: A–B, 18: I, 30: I)
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="6555FF2AFFE7FFD8FF71FF0CFED0FECA" blockId="15.[151,1437,150,357]" pageId="15" pageNumber="16">
This species is most similar to 
<taxonomicName id="A2EA84A9FFE7FFD8FE16FF0DFD54FF56" box="[496,681,222,248]" class="Insecta" family="Noctuidae" genus="Eudocima" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="15" pageNumber="16" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="kinabaluensis">
<emphasis id="579E2338FFE7FFD8FE16FF0DFD54FF56" box="[496,681,222,248]" italics="true" pageId="15" pageNumber="16">E. kinabaluensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
but the forewing differs by a smooth outer margin and the shape of the green patch from base to subterminal area (
<bibRefCitation id="017B82DBFFE7FFD8FD4CFED0FC94FEB2" author="Yoshimoto, H." box="[682,873,258,284]" pageId="15" pageNumber="16" pagination="60 - 62" refId="ref41277" refString="Yoshimoto, H. (1999) A new species of the genus Othreis Hubner (Noctuidae, Ophiderinae) from Myanmar. Transactions of the Lepidopterological Society of Japan, 50 (1), 60 - 62." type="journal article" year="1999">Yoshimoto 1999</bibRefCitation>
). The distal side of the dark discal stigma extends anteriorly as a short projection. This species is only recorded from northern 
<collectingCountry id="1DFDBFBAFFE7FFD8FC02FEF5FBACFEEF" box="[996,1105,295,321]" name="Myanmar" pageId="15" pageNumber="16">Myanmar</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation id="017B82DBFFE7FFD8FBB9FEF4FAE7FEEE" author="Yoshimoto, H." box="[1119,1306,294,320]" pageId="15" pageNumber="16" pagination="60 - 62" refId="ref41277" refString="Yoshimoto, H. (1999) A new species of the genus Othreis Hubner (Noctuidae, Ophiderinae) from Myanmar. Transactions of the Lepidopterological Society of Japan, 50 (1), 60 - 62." type="journal article" year="1999">Yoshimoto 1999</bibRefCitation>
) and northern 
<collectingCountry id="1DFDBFBAFFE7FFD8FF27FE98FED5FECA" box="[193,296,330,356]" name="Thailand" pageId="15" pageNumber="16">Thailand</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
